<span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose nulldelimiter"></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p>它的 <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>L</mi><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">L1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">L</span><span class="mord">1</span></span></span></span> 范数有一个简单的形式</p>
<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msub><mrow><mo fence="true">∥</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">∂</mi><mi>p</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">∂</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo fence="true">∥</mo></mrow><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><munder><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>j</mi></mrow></munder><mrow><mo fence="true">∣</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">∂</mi><msub><mi>p</mi><mi>i</mi></msub></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">∂</mi><msub><mi>x</mi><mi>j</mi></msub></mrow></mfrac><mo fence="true">∣</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><munder><mo>∑</mo><mi>i</mi></munder><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msub><mi>p</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><mo>−</mo><msubsup><mi>p</mi><mi>i</mi><mn>2</mn></msubsup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><munder><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo mathvariant="normal">≠</mo><mi>j</mi></mrow></munder><msub><mi>p</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><msub><mi>p</mi><mi>j</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><munder><mo>∑</mo><mi>i</mi></munder><msubsup><mi>p</mi><mi>i</mi><mn>2</mn></msubsup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\frac{1}{2} \left\| \frac{\partial p}{\partial x} \right\|_1 = \frac{1}{2} \sum_{i,j} \left| \frac{\partial p_i}{\partial x_j} \right|
= \frac{1}{2} \sum_i (p_i - p_i^2) + \frac{1}{2} \sum_{i \neq j} p_i p_j = 1 - \sum_i p_i^2
